params._amountIn: The amount of a certain token provided
params._assetIn: The address of the token provided
params._assetOut: The address of the token desired
params._destination: The address to send swapped funds to (must be payable)
params._poolId: Address of the pool to perform swaps
params._priceTokenIn: Price of tokenIn in USD, times 1e12
params._priceTokenOut: Price of tokenOut in USD, times 1e12
params._slippageFactor: The tolerable slippage expressed as the numerator over 1000. E.g. 950 => 950/1000 => 5% slippage tolerance
